data.description: 3.375% FHA assumable financing available....ask Listing Agent for details.  Priced under market value this home is being offered with a roof replacement and a $3,000 flooring with acceptable offer.   Tour this Ashwood Forest Subdivision home located on a quiet cul-de-sac street and in the award-winning Penn Harris Madison ‘PHM’ School District.  With just under 2,500 total finished sqft this home has 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a finished basement.  There is lots of living spaces including an open concept kitchen & family room with gas log fireplace, dining room, living room/den, and two additional finished lower-level rooms (what’s on your wish list . . . a rec room, playroom, or workout room).  The master suite boasts a double vanity and two walk-in closets. There’s a 19 x13 deck to relax and enjoy the fully fenced-in backyard. The septic has been pre-inspected and newer mechanicals include: HVAC systems 2018, water heater 2022, dishwasher 2019, refrigerator 2016. With newer major mechanicals and possibly a new roof you could be spending your time, resources and creativity to make this home your personal special place to live.
